## Get Dashboard Categories

Returns a breakdown of records grouped by category, including totals and percentage distribution. Used to render pie/donut charts on the dashboard.

**Access:** Admin, Analyst, Viewer (all authenticated users)

### Response Examples

**200 OK**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "categories": [
      {
        "category": "income",
        "total": 450000,
        "count": 24,
        "percentage": 61.6
      },
      {
        "category": "expense",
        "total": 182000,
        "count": 28,
        "percentage": 24.9
      },
      {
        "category": "investment",
        "total": 95000,
        "count": 6,
        "percentage": 13.5
      }
    ],
    "grandTotal": 727000
  }
}
```

**401 Unauthorized**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Authentication required. Please log in."
}
```

**500 Internal Server Error**
```json
{
  "success": false,
  "message": "Internal server error. Please try again later."
}
```

## Get Recent Activity

Returns the most recently created or updated records. Used to populate the "Recent Activity" feed on the dashboard.

**Access:** Admin, Analyst, Viewer (all authenticated users)

### Query Parameters
| Parameter | Type | Required | Default | Description |
|-----------|------|----------|---------|-------------|
| limit | number | No | 5 | Number of recent records to return (max 20) |

### Response Examples

**200 OK**
```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "recentActivity": [
      {
        "_id": "69ce74c8f1fd65f7789f5085",
        "title": "Monthly Salary - April 2026",
        "amount": 80000,
        "category": "income",
        "date": "2026-04-01T00:00:00.000Z",
        "createdBy": {
          "_id": "69cd709ef6d0d02290c9de6e",
          "name": "Suraj Sharma"
        },
        "createdAt": "2026-04-04T10:00:00.000Z"
      },
      {
        "_id": "69ce74c8f1fd65f7789f5086",
        "title": "Office Supplies",
        "amount": 3200,
        "category": "expense",
        "date": "2026-04-03T00:00:00.000Z",
        "createdBy": {
          "_id": "69ce1b3e09f4a12390c9ab1f",
          "name": "Priya Mehta"
        },
        "createdAt": "2026-04-03T09:15:00.000Z"
      }
    ]
  }
}
```

